{"number":99,"name":"سُورَةُ الزَّلۡزَلَةِ","englishName":"Az-Zalzala","englishNameTranslation":"The Earthquake","revelationType":"Medinan","ayahs":[{"number":6139,"text":"When the earth is shaken with its [final] earthquake","numberInSurah":1,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false},{"number":6140,"text":"And the earth discharges its burdens","numberInSurah":2,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false},{"number":6141,"text":"And man says, \"What is [wrong] with it?\" -","numberInSurah":3,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false},{"number":6142,"text":"That Day, it will report its news","numberInSurah":4,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false},{"number":6143,"text":"Because your Lord has commanded it.","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false},{"number":6144,"text":"That Day, the people will depart separated [into categories] to be shown [the result of] their deeds.","numberInSurah":6,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false},{"number":6145,"text":"So whoever does an atom's weight of good will see it,","numberInSurah":7,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false},{"number":6146,"text":"And whoever does an atom's weight of evil will see it.","numberInSurah":8,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":599,"ruku":541,"hizbQuarter":239,"sajda":false}]}